msgid "Emacs represents each terminal as a @dfn{terminal object} data type (@pxref{Terminal Type}).  On GNU and Unix systems, Emacs can use multiple terminals simultaneously in each session.  On other systems, it can only use a single terminal.  Each terminal object has the following attributes:"
